title: Flight Simulator 2020  - Addon spotlight - UH 1C Huey Gunship - version 1.0
description:
In this video we will look at the UH 1C Hue Gunship helicopter. The helicopter has been recently released but it still under development. To use it you will need to install AirlandFS and load the profile which is included in the zip file.

After we looked at how to load the AirlandFS profile we look at the exterior of the helicopter before we jump into the cockpit. Once we reviewed everything we take the helicopter out for a small ride.

If you also want to give this aircraft a try download your own copy from:
https://flightsim.to/file/24313/uh-1c-huey-gunship
